- A simple way to do so would be to decorate your view with the preflight view directly;
- Otherwise, by default, if it's an OPTION that's being defined, it might make sense to decorate it with the preflight view before registering the two. This behaviour should be configurable (with a `add_cors_preflight` flag that could be set to either `True` or `False`).

